{"tid":1459693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[跪求推到上熱門]想問下有冇巴絲睇過SCMP樓下d cm","createTime":"2019-08-12T19:10:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T01:09:57.000Z","uid":265508,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2a15f3ca18b6768fdb73ed09e87fc376caeb8792","tid":1459693,"uid":265508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:10:45.000Z","msg":"P牌仔第一次出文要屌屌細力d<br />\n<br />\n今日出機場想搵英文文宣就睇下SCMP fb<br />\n唔睇由自可<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一睇d外國狗支那蝗<br />\n原來一個二個乜9都唔知就喺度9up</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以下係其中幾個post幾個cm:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O47LoD2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO47LoD2.jpg&h=5dca7d33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6HZYJEO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6HZYJEO.jpg&h=d9bba9b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ni9JUMN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fni9JUMN.jpg&h=6a0e8aba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f4V1Gr9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff4V1Gr9.jpg&h=e4722312&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老味睇到我好撚火滾</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係佢屋企既事佢自然唔會關注咁多<br />\n跟住就斷章取義<br />\n今朝見到有個美國閪話我地成班youngsters玩real life Clash of the Titans<br />\n我玩佢條撚毛咩<br />\n熱死辣辣full gear 好撚好玩啊?<br />\n跟住小妹就長文怒屌佢<br />\n然後啱先想搵番佢cm就搵唔到鳥<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以想請各位可唔可以盡量喺SCMP同其他外國媒體d fb cm洗下版po下文宣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔想d外國花生友/支那狗再乜9都唔知就話我地廢青搞亂香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要比佢地知道今時今日搞成咁係因為黑警<br />\n因為柒婆<br />\n因為共匪!!!<br />\n<br />\n我地可以成個故事由2014甚至1997開始講到8.11!<br />\n用網上力量+頭版+機場旅客嚟拉國際支持啊!!!<br />\n<br />\n跪求英文好既巴絲出一分力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbetween有啱用文宣都可以貼喺度<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家一齊努力洗版!</span></span>"},{"pid":"67f0c3550e0f7d34383b7f24f7dc342bb98371e3","tid":1459693,"uid":265508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:11:54.000Z","msg":"自推十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3cdc297499fb286408f9e2a2ae0231d2468dd53","tid":1459693,"uid":265508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:12:16.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"de9bdd063a270643aa89eb425ccef76bcfc83134","tid":1459693,"uid":265508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:12:40.000Z","msg":"二"},{"pid":"a129679891ed720272b60ad084c18be71b7c99d4","tid":1459693,"uid":116491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:12:49.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"bb885dfba854a138f45b1fa5a761db2e7703e72c","tid":1459693,"uid":265508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:13:01.000Z","msg":"三"},{"pid":"4efda1b283310d16c45ab539c7df9e0fe70896ba","tid":1459693,"uid":265508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:13:11.000Z","msg":"四"},{"pid":"7cd2b2d11ad240067511c48f72473dfc9a82ff00","tid":1459693,"uid":265508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:13:23.000Z","msg":"五"},{"pid":"038c5d1abf207326c2ee9de0752cba17f6c71296","tid":1459693,"uid":265508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:13:34.000Z","msg":"六"},{"pid":"67e7bc9b72e9b7f0809d1986788e790308070593","tid":1459693,"uid":265508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:13:45.000Z","msg":"七"},{"pid":"7a8a5a82c8e88509abd8f8ab99e6475cb357b5f3","tid":1459693,"uid":265508,"li